=======================================================================
=======								=======
=======				dbTools				=======
=======								=======
=======================================================================

Personnal stuff, configurations files, usefull scripts, ...



.:

conf/			-> Configurations files (~/.stuff)

scripts/		-> Scripts (I am used to put them in /usr/local/sbin)



./conf:

.bashrc			-> Bash aliases

.gitconfig		-> Git username



./scripts:

clean.sh*		-> "Clean" remove '*~', '#*#', '*.o' recursively

gs.sh*			-> "Grep Safe" is like grep but ignore binary files
			   and stuff (svn, git, ...)

fgs.sh*			-> "File Grep Safe" open files resulting from gs.sh

ippriv.sh*		-> "IP Private" display your private IP

ippub.sh*		-> "IP Public" display your public IP

newCproject.sh*		-> Create a directory which contain files to start
			   a C project in db0 style.

replaceall.sh*		-> Replace a word in all files recursively



